  "body": "Might be helpful for there to be a note in documentation (either on the trufflesuite.com, maybe the v4 branch somewhere, or elsewhere) for truffle v4 users to now use an older stable web3 0.20 compatible `truffle-hdwallet-provider` when doing \"live\" network migrations.\r\n\r\n`npm i truffle-hdwallet-provider` now defaults to a Web3 1.0 compatible pkg, which won't work with truffle v4 (uses web3 0.20).",
